    </p>

    <p class="mb-6">
      Of course, one could navigate to the graph for the next grid and make O&M plans like that, but that’s not a scalable approach. In all likelihood, mini-grid developers will have hundreds of sites under management in a few years. For scale, we need a single interface that it is simple, intuitive, and actionable.       
